==Overview==
The Run Forwarding Feed provides run submission data to clients (non-team typically).  The Run Forward Feed data includes both run information (Team, Problem, etc) and the submitted source code file(s).

== Getting the feed ==

A client will read the data from a socket on the CCS, a port number is defined in the [[Contest_Control_System#contest.yaml|contest.yaml]]
file <tt>submission-feed-port</tt> entry.

===Authentication===

:No authentication is required.  

== File format ==

:The event feed is an XML document within the root element <tt><runs></tt>.

 <runs version="1.0">
   <run-submission... />
   <run-submission... />
   <run-submission... />
 </runs>

;version: the format version. Must be "1.0"

All events are separate elements at the top level.

